reviews.review_text: Borrowed instruments show Thank you for the upload!

Intimate This is the closest you'll ever get to hearing the Dead playing a personal show for you at your house. It has the vibe of a group of guys jamming at their friends' party. Just laid back, loose, and fun. The crowd loves it. A very special show and a must-hear!
